Birthday wish

index.html
```
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <title>Birthday Wish</title>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
    <audio id="birthdayAudio" preload="auto">
        <source src="favsong.mp3" type="audio/mpeg">
        Your browser does not support the audio element.
    </audio>
</head>
<body>
    <h1><i>Happy Birthday Teju...🎀</i></h1>

    <div class="message">
    <p>Wishing you a day filled with love, joy, and all your favorite things. May this year bring you happiness and success in everything you do. Enjoy your special day!</p>
    </div>

    <div class="button">
        <button onclick="song()" style="font-size: 1.2em; padding: 15px 30px;">Click to play</button>
    </div>

    <div class="cd-container">
        <div class="cd-disc"></div>
    </div>

    <script src="script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
```

